						               													<description>The ancient reptilian civilization of the Sarens disappeared millions years ago. They knew all about matter manipulation and hyperspace travel. The remains of this civilization plunge into oblivion are spread across Heos&amp;rsquo;s realms and are full of powerful relics that defy the imagination.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Expeditions have engaged in an archaeological journey on behalf of powerful factions and their members will use all of their abilities to achieve their ends. For prophecy is that when enough relics have been found, a dimensional portal will open to go on the moon Wym, the cradle of the Secret of the Sarens...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player leads an expedition in order to collect Sarens relics. Expeditions are made of 3 type of cards: Regions, Classes &amp;amp; Factions: &amp;#10;&amp;#10;     On each Region card, you will find 2 to 4 relics.&amp;#10;     Each Class card has only 1 relic, but it is balanced by abilities like looking at the other players cards or destroying a type of card.&amp;#10;     Each Faction has a permanent effect that can reverse the situation.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players will activate their cards in order to find more Relics than the other players and try to guess the other player's score in order to end the game at the right time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
